OL,3,CPolice hunt for stolen Superlambanana
OL,5,FThis particular replica has a rainbow
OL,6,Fcoat and a large white handprint
OL,7,Facross its centre. It's said to have
OL,8,F"sentimental value" to the family, who
OL,9,Fare keen for its return.
OL,11,FIt was inspired by the original
OL,12,FSuperlambanana, which was created in
OL,13,F1998 by Japanese artist Taro Chiezo as
OL,14,Fpart of the ArtTranspennine
OL,15,FExhibition. The sculpture, which is
OL,16,Fmeant to be a cross between a banana
OL,17,Fand a lamb, is said to represent
OL,18,FLiverpool's history of cargo imports
OL,19,Fand comment on genetic engineering.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
